eZ DBug extension v0.0.1 README

What is the eZ DBug extension?
================================

eZ DBug is a true eZ publish extension
that provides simple, styled variable 
dump debug output features.

These features are available as 
template operators and php class object methods.

This code is very simple to customize to meet your own tastes and needs!

{$take_that_stale_ol|attribute(show,1)}!


eZ DBug version
=======================

The current version of eZ DBug is 0.0.1.
Last Updated: January 13, 2007

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.0.1


